social_posts.post_text: Camping under the stars with llamas on the Inca Trail to Machu Picchu 🥾✨⛰️

location.city_name: Machu Picchu, Peru - Wonder Of The World

social_posts.post_text:
Finally made it out to see one of the 7 Wonders of the World 💚

Machu Picchu - an astonishing 15th century citadel from the Inca Empire up on a 2430 meter mountain ridge ⛰️

Got lucky with clear skies and breathtaking views! It’s currently winter, where it is dry, but cold in the morning and at night. Acclimating to the altitude was clutch in completing the 4D/3N trek 🥾

View of Machu Picchu from Waynapicchu and Sun Gate! 

Pretty cool to see it featured in the new Transformers that just released 🦍🎥

Back to back 4-day treks. Next up, Ausangate! The 5th highest mountain in Peru ⛺️🇵🇪🏔️ 

I got very lucky with an amazing guide @exploroads 🎒
“Nature is the purest portal to inner-peace.” 🙇🏻‍♂️🏞️
The variety of landscapes in Peru feel like from a different planet 👽
Getting up early to beat the crowds is my favorite way to enjoy nature 😛🌈⛰️
Tried to show my mom why I’ll never give up the drop top life… she was briefly amused and still doesn’t approve 😆🏎️🌅
